prompts.frontCover: Vibrant and dynamic comic book style greeting card. The scene is a sunny beach with bright blue sky and stylized waves. A comic book action panel shows Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo, illustrated as superheroes. Lao Lao is in the foreground, striking a powerful and confident pose with a joyful, laughing expression. She's wearing a superhero version of her blue sweatshirt, complete with a flowing cape and a custom emblem on the chest that combines a dog paw print and a sun. Jordan is behind her, cheering her on with an enthusiastic expression, wearing a superhero version of his brown hoodie. Surrounding them are two small, adorable superhero dogs, one a fluffy white poodle mix and the other a scruffy terrier mix, both wearing tiny capes and masks, joyfully leaping in the air. Action words like "KAPOW!" and "BIRTHDAY BLAST!" pop around the scene in classic comic book style lettering. In the center of the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday to my Super Girlfriend!". The entire composition is energetic, colorful, and fun, with bold outlines and Ben-Day dot patterns in the background. Flat 2D artwork for printing.
